# Pretty.af Design System

## Brand Identity
- **Name**: Pretty.af
- **Tagline**: "AI-Powered Image Generation Marketplace"
- **Personality**: Modern, Creative, Accessible, Social-First

## Color System

### Primary Colors
```css
:root {
  /* Pretty.af Brand Colors */
  --pretty-primary: #6366f1; /* Indigo - main brand color */
  --pretty-primary-hover: #4f46e5;
  --pretty-primary-light: #a5b4fc;
  
  /* Social Authentication Colors */
  --twitter-blue: #1da1f2;
  --twitter-blue-hover: #1a91da;
  --google-red: #ea4335;
  --google-red-hover: #d33b2c;
  
  /* Status Colors */
  --success: #10b981;
  --warning: #f59e0b;
  --error: #ef4444;
  --info: #3b82f6;
}
```

### Neutral Colors (Tailwind-based)
```css
