### Component Spacing Guidelines
- **Card padding**: `p-6` (24px)
- **Button padding**: `px-4 py-2` (16px/8px)
- **Section spacing**: `py-12` (48px)
- **Element gaps**: `gap-4` or `gap-6` (16px/24px)

## Component Patterns

### Button Hierarchy
```tsx
// Primary Action (X/Twitter OAuth)
